s; players can use any combination of them to form their own unique fighting style and clever use of different ways to fight with the enemy. Players need to observe different enemy fighting ways to make different combat changes after a long time of training and combat to grow into a qualified \"Subspace hunter\" to protect our reality plane.", "short_description": "Subspace Hunter is an MR+VR dual-mode action game; players need to use guns, blades, superpowers and any combination of the invasion of the subspace into the real world of the epic battle. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sh.xuking.tech/privacy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Meta developer hub", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sh.xuking.tech/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "3744040075834813"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7593229157407973"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "813819567217251"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "813819567217251"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1707505333, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "813819567217251"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "9467844446613092", "version": "0.2.4.3"}, "id": "2104004773284191", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus